                            <comment id="15011160" author="christopher.l.shannon" created="Wed, 18 Nov 2015 15:11:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gtully&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gtully&quot;&gt;gtully&lt;/a&gt;, Mind taking a look at this to make sure the fix looks good?  It was a simple one line fix in DemandForwardingBridgeSupport and I think it&apos;s fine.  I included a test case (NetworkDurableRecreationTest) with 4 tests that all break without this fix, but pass with it.  In the meantime, I&apos;m going to let Jenkins run and see if this change causes other issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
